			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64541911">		
		on Tuesday June 11, 2024 @06:49PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//tech.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23353771&amp;cid=64541911">#64541911</a>)
		<small><a href="http://slashdot.org/" title="http://slashdot.org/" class="user_homepage_display">Homepage</a>
